OL,3,C'Her smile lit up a room': Family's
OL,4,Ctribute to murdered mother following
OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,FLorna England's daughter Jackie Baxter
OL,8,Fread out a family statement following
OL,9,Fthe end of the inquest
OL,11,FThe family of a grandmother stabbed to
OL,12,Fdeath in a random, frenzied attack in
OL,13,FExeter two years ago have told ITV
OL,14,FNews they relive the horror of her
OL,15,Fdeath every single day.
OL,17,FLorna England, who was 74, was killed
OL,18,Fin Ludwell Valley Park while walking
OL,19,Fhome from the supermarket. Last year
OL,20,FCameron Davis was jailed for life for
OL,21,Fher murder.
