OL,3,C'Her smile lit up a room': Family's
OL,4,Ctribute to murdered mother following
OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,FAn inquest examining the actions of
OL,8,Femergency services in the lead-up to
OL,9,Fthe fatal attack has been held at
OL,10,FExeter and Greater Devon Coroner's
OL,11,FCourt.
OL,13,FThe proceedings concluded today, with
OL,14,Fa coroner ruling that she was
OL,15,Funlawfully killed.
OL,17,FIn a statement read out by Ms
OL,18,FEngland's family, they said: "Lorna
OL,19,Fwas the beloved wife of fifty-two
OL,20,Fyears, mother and grandmother and
OL,21,Fsister.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
