OL,3,C'Her smile lit up a room': Family's
OL,4,Ctribute to murdered mother following
OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,F"She was a kind and loving lady who
OL,8,Flived life to the full, and was the
OL,9,Fmost content person you would ever
OL,10,Fwish to meet, her smile lit up the
OL,11,Froom and her gentle nature made
OL,12,Feveryone feel welcomed and loved.
OL,14,F"The family want to express their
OL,15,Fgratitude to the emergency services
OL,16,Fwho helped Lorna, we have a permanent
OL,17,Fempty void because we miss Lorna so
OL,18,Fmuch, we will never come to terms with
OL,19,Fher loss, how do you come to terms
OL,20,Fwith such a wicked act?"
