OL,7,FBackground to the case
OL,9,FDuring the trial, Miss Jo Martin, KC,
OL,10,Fprosecuting, told the court that Mrs
OL,11,FEngland left home to walk to Lidl to
OL,12,Fbuy flour on the afternoon of 18
OL,13,FFebruary, leaving her husband David,
OL,14,Fto whom she had been married for 52
OL,15,Fyears, waiting for her at home.
OL,17,FShe was killed on a path in woodland
OL,18,Fby Davis, who had been wandering
OL,19,Faround at the back of the Wonford
OL,20,FSports Centre for more than half an
OL,21,Fhour while drinking vodka.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
