OL,7,FShe suffered a non-fatal wound to her
OL,8,Fneck, a fatal wound to her chest and
OL,9,Fdefensive wounds on her hands.
OL,11,FThe attack was witnessed by a dog
OL,12,Fwalker who at first thought she saw
OL,13,Ftwo people dancing but then realised
OL,14,Fit was one blocking the other's path.
OL,16,FShe heard Mrs England cry out and fall
OL,17,Fto the ground.
