OL,7,FDavis took her phone and told the
OL,8,Fwitness, in a matter-of-fact way, that
OL,9,Fthe injured woman had suffered a fit
OL,10,Fand she needed to call an ambulance.
OL,12,FHe dropped the knife in a brook, the
OL,13,Fphone nearby, and a hoodie as he
OL,14,Fwalked out of the park onto Hazel Road.
OL,16,FThe court was told that Davis was
OL,17,Fliving in temporary accommodation
OL,18,Fprovided by a housing association,
OL,19,Fhaving been homeless in Exeter when he
OL,20,Fmoved there from Bournemouth.
