OL,7,FOn January 23, he asked to talk to his
OL,8,Fsupport workers because his mental
OL,9,Fhealth was deteriorating, saying he
OL,10,Fwould either hurt himself or someone
OL,11,Felse.
OL,13,FHe was assessed by two psychiatrists
OL,14,Fon 28 January, who both decided he did
OL,15,Fnot need to be sectioned.
OL,17,FDavis began expressing his love for
OL,18,Fhis support worker between 9 and 16
OL,19,FFebruary and was seen by the mental
OL,20,Fhealth team who decided he did not
OL,21,Fneed to be sectioned.
