OL,7,FHe was then given seven days' notice
OL,8,Fto leave his accommodation.
OL,10,FHe told officers and ambulance crew he
OL,11,Fwould commit a crime if he was not
OL,12,Fdetained.
OL,14,FMiss Martin said: "He said he was
OL,15,Fgoing to kill someone if he was
OL,16,Freleased that day.
OL,18,F"He said he had committed crimes in
OL,19,Fthe past and always got away with it.
OL,20,FHe repeated that if he was discharged
OL,21,Fhe would kill a random person."
