OL,7,FMs Martin said Davis called police at
OL,8,F4.41am on the morning of 18 February `
OL,9,Fthe day he attacked Mrs England ` and
OL,10,Fthreatened to take his own life in a
OL,11,Ffire at his accommodation unless he
OL,12,Fwas arrested.
OL,14,FParamedics and police attended the
OL,15,Fproperty, where they found Davis
OL,16,Fsitting on the pavement outside.
OL,18,F"He said he was going to kill someone
OL,19,Fif he was discharged that day," Ms
OL,20,FMartin told the court.
