OL,7,F"He said he had committed other crimes
OL,8,Fin the past and always got away with
OL,9,Fit. He repeated that if he was
OL,10,Fdischarged, he would kill a random
OL,11,Fperson."
OL,13,FDavis was taken to the Royal Devon and
OL,14,FExeter Hospital, where he was told
OL,15,Fthat if he did anything it would be a
OL,16,Fpre-meditated crime.
OL,18,FTwo psychiatrists discussed whether to
OL,19,Fsection Davis and decided that he did
OL,20,Fnot need to be admitted to hospital.
