OL,7,FHe later bought vodka and a knife at a
OL,8,FLidl supermarket and went to Ludwell
OL,9,FValley Park, where he fatally attacked
OL,10,FMrs England and took her mobile phone.
OL,12,FAfter leaving the park, Davis went to
OL,13,Fshops and two pubs in Exeter before
OL,14,Fbeing spotted on CCTV sitting on the
OL,15,Fpavement in the city centre at 9.30pm.
OL,17,FHe was arrested on suspicion of
OL,18,Fmurder, telling police: "I f*****
OL,19,Fwarned you c****, that's why I f******
OL,20,Fdone it. I didn't want to but none of
OL,21,Fyou f****** c**** listened."
