OL,7,FThe trial also heard from two
OL,8,Fpsychiatrists ` one who said Davis had
OL,9,Fa schizoaffective disorder and a
OL,10,Fsecond who said he had a personality
OL,11,Fdisorder which made him "manipulative
OL,12,Fand angry" when combined with drug and
OL,13,Falcohol abuse.
OL,15,FDavis was convicted of her murder and
OL,16,Fjailed for 28 years at Exeter Crown
OL,17,FCourt in July 2024.
